message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present this extraordinary product to you. It's not just an item; it's a valuable asset that could significantly enhance your life or business. Considering its exceptional quality and unique features, I believe it's worth more than its face value. I am offering it to you for $12000. This is a special opportunity to acquire something truly remarkable at a price that reflects its true worth. I look forward to hearing your thoughts on this offer.
